{"tid":249584,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"FB 被判罰 1.1 億歐元！歐盟：買下 WhatsApp 不代表可使用個人資料","createTime":"2017-05-19T11:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T16:30:50.000Z","uid":1130,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77e99e968d034d5ca24a7562646d7a46abaf425f","tid":249584,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"近日路透社報導，本周四歐盟反壟斷機構對 Facebook 判罰款 1.1 億歐元，因為 Facebook 於 2014 年時以 218 億收購 WhatsApp 之後，Facebook 當時在收購聲明中表示，將不會把 Facebook 與 WhatsApp 兩者的用戶進行自動配對，以收集用戶的個人資料。不過卻在 2 年後推出一項功能，完全違反了早年作出的聲明，歐盟因此展開調查，而 Facebook 亦在交易等待審批期間接連 2 次提供誤導性資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/facebook-whatsapp.png?ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Ffacebook-whatsapp.png%3Fssl%3D1&h=03856c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐盟對此表示，這次的罰款是要向企業傳達一個明確的訊息，各企業需要遵守歐盟收購的所有規則，包括提供正確資訊，對於 Facebook 所判罰的夥款是適當而具有威懾作用的。不過有消息指出，歐盟的罰款金額的最高上限本來應佔 Facebook 營業額的 1％，亦即 2.48 億歐元，但是這次所判罰的款項 1.1 億歐元是遠低於這個上限。相信歐盟這次的做法，是要阻止 Facebook 繼續向用戶取得更多的個人資料，亦防止其他公司的效法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/05/19/facebook-110-million-euro/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2Ffacebook-110-million-euro%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a32b6d58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/05/19/facebook-110-million-euro/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db20d4033e48c76537b1d45047f4c857b57d8e26","tid":249584,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:58:54.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<br />\n垃圾fb整到wts成日壞又更新埋d廢野<br />\n又抄snapchat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c3107ebdf9e39dcd1d021dc6dfc4f464f8e750","tid":249584,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"e家個messager,ig,wts,fb炒埋一堆咁<br />\n又成日彈apps<br />\n都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab01798692e58b3c7a6d104769580918f814e25f","tid":249584,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:03:38.000Z","msg":"telegram係清泉，到底班撚樣幾時醒"},{"pid":"95861e751c0c0a1a7b0865f59c478e340ca0ac66","tid":249584,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>telegram係清泉，到底班撚樣幾時醒</blockquote><br />\n好用好多<br />\n又可以sd返野俾自己<br />\nwts最近更新個pin都係抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0beacb4fecf2c09b52acc95939b536adad744744","tid":249584,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a6be1dbb56ef6fdad45d69ee100ad41930022f0","tid":249584,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>telegram係清泉，到底班撚樣幾時醒</blockquote><br />\n好用好多<br />\n又可以sd返野俾自己<br />\nwts最近更新個pin都係抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntelegram直頭叫自己果度叫cloud storage<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8031a37e562e738f22845aea83648c90e751400","tid":249584,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"歐盟：肥肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02abec43c16e7cabdf6b4f4759d7294cb5b296c4","tid":249584,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:18:17.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp加撚埋啲垃圾功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  基本野又唔做好啲"},{"pid":"4471c27a638cc6ef1956627e9